---
layout: base
permalink: "/"
---

<div class="home-intro">
  {{ content | safe }}
</div>
<h2 class='projects-heading'>Case Studies</h2>

<p>Deep dives into my projects, read on to find out about how I approach UX Design in a project and all about my process.<p>
{% set caseStudies = collections.caseStudies %}
<ul class='case-studies'>
{% for project in caseStudies %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ project.url }}">
                 {% if project.data.icon %}
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            src="/media/{{ project.data.icon }}"
            alt=""
            class='case-studies-icon'
          >
          {% endif %}
        <div class='case-studies-text'>
        <h3>{{ project.data.title | safe }}  ↗</h3>
        <p>{{ project.data.description | safe }}</p>
        </div>
        </a>
      </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
<h2 class='projects-heading'>Concepts</h1>
<p>Sometimes, I make up concepts for apps based on gaps I see, or ideas I have, read one of these to find out more about my process, the kinds of projects I'd love to work on, and hopefuly something that might spark something in you too!<p>
{% set conceptProjects = collections.concept %}
<ul class='concepts'>
  {% for project in conceptProjects %}
    {% if project.inputPath.includes('/projects/') %}
      <li>
    <a href="{{ project.url }}">
       {% if project.data.icon %}
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            src="/media/{{ project.data.icon }}"
            alt=""
            class='concepts-icon'
          >
          {% endif %}
<div class='concepts-text'>
        <h3>{{ project.data.title | safe }}  ↗</h3>
    <p>{{ project.data.description | safe }}</p>
    </div>
    </a>
      </li>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
<h2 class='projects-heading'>Explorations</h1>
<p>A space for me to explore different designs.</p>
{% set explorationsProjects = collections.exploration %}
<ul class='grid'>
  {% for project in explorationsProjects %}
    {% if project.inputPath.includes('/projects/') %}
      <li class='explorations'>
        <a href="{{ project.url }}">
          {% if project.data.image %}
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            src="/media/{{ project.data.image }}"
            alt=""
            class='explorations-img'
          >
          {% endif %}
          <h3>{{ project.data.title | safe }}  ↗</h3>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</ul>